data.description: Pristine home that is nestled in on a little piece of serenity. 4 bedrooms and 2 1/2 bathrooms all on easy one level living. So many recent updates including new exterior paint throughout and all new windows. You are immediately welcomed to the large living room with a cozy wood burning fireplace. Kitchen opens to the dining room.  Kitchen has been recently updated with new granite counters, backsplash and stainless appliances. All new lighting fixtures, laminate, carpet and interior doors throughout. Large family room that lends the perfect space for entertaining, complete with pellet stove and doors that open up to the patio.  Bonus room with sink that would be the perfect space for a wet bar, etc. Primary suite with bathroom. Detached 2 car garage, ample storage in shed and additional covered parking. The Pristine grounds complete with large patio and beautiful koi pond.  Enjoy the quiet and country life while only a few minutes from shopping, schools and parks.
